{
  "name": "SMSCRM v4.0 - Test Basic",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## ðŸ§ª SMS Test System v4.0 - Basic Test\n\n**Purpose:**\n- âœ… Test basic workflow without AI\n- âœ… Verify API endpoints work\n- âœ… Simple auto-reply\n- âœ… Easy to debug\n\n**How it works:**\n- Polls every 30 seconds\n- Gets recent messages\n- Filters for unread inbound\n- Sends simple auto-reply\n- Marks as read",
        "height": 500,
        "width": 600,
        "color": 6
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -1000,
        -200
      ],
      "id": "workflow-info",
      "name": "Workflow Information"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "rule": {
          "interval": [
            {
              "field": "seconds",
              "secondsInterval": 30
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "id": "poll-trigger",
      "name": "Poll Every 30s",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.scheduleTrigger",
      "typeVersion": 1.2,
      "position": [
        -800,
        200
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "url": "https://smsn8n.marketsuite.co/api/messages/recent?limit=50",
        "options": {
          "timeout": 10000
        }
      },
      "id": "get-messages",
      "name": "Get Recent Messages",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [
        -600,
        200
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "// Filter for unread inbound messages\nconst messages = $input.all();\nconst unreadMessages = [];\n\nfor (const message of messages) {\n  if (message.json.direction === 'inbound' && message.json.status === 'unread') {\n    unreadMessages.push(message.json);\n  }\n}\n\nreturn unreadMessages.map(msg => ({ json: msg }));"
      },
      "id": "filter-unread",
      "name": "Filter Unread Messages",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        -400,
        200
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "values": {
          "string": [
            {
              "name": "reply_message",
              "value": "Thanks for your message! This is an automated reply from the SMS system. Your message was: {{ $json.content }}"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "prepare-reply",
